comments: Adams (MEM) firms up on his right leg and marginal contact occurs as LeVert (CLE) moves over the pick.
Mobley (CLE) lightly brushes Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) right arm and marginal contact occurs during his play at the basket.
Okoro (CLE) makes incidental hand-on-ball contact with Jackson Jr. (MEM) when the ball is dislodged during his play at the basket.
Morant (MEM) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Okoro (CLE) legally contests Morant's (MEM) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly grasps Mobley's (CLE) jersey and immediately releases it as marginal contact occurs during the pursuit of the rebound.
Brooks (MEM) grasps and immediately releases Garland's (CLE) jersey during the drive and the contact is marginal.
Adams (MEM) legally contests Mobley's (CLE) shot attempt in the paint.
A Delay of Game warning is issued to Cleveland for making illegal contact with the ball after a successful shot attempt.
Bane (MEM) cuts behind Okoro (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as he slides his hand off of the defender.
Adams (MEM) establishes himself in a legal screening position and does not deliver contact to Okoro (CLE) when setting the pick.
Allen (CLE) extends his right leg out and shifts his body weight into Morant (MEM) and initiates contact that impacts Morant's SQBR.
Brooks (MEM) and Garland (CLE) come together away from the ball and the contact is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) legally contests Garland's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) lightly brushes Mobley's (CLE) side during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) jumps alongside Garland's (CLE) path and gets to ball height and cleanly blocks Garland's driving shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes last contact with the ball prior to it going out of bounds and possession is properly retained by Cleveland.
Okoro (CLE) is not able to inbound the ball within five seconds after receiving it from the official. Possession is properly awarded to Memphis.
Bane (MEM) and LeVert (CLE) engage and disengage during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
LeVert (CLE) establishes himself in Brooks' (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as Brooks fights over the screen.
Adams (MEM) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Okoro (CLE) jumps alongside Morant (MEM) and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) avoids making contact with Morant's (MEM) arm during his contest of the driving shot attempt.
Mobley (CLE) lightly brushes Adams' (MEM) back during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Adams' (MEM) layup attempt at the basket.
Brooks (MEM) and Garland (CLE) engage and disengage during the inbound and the contact is marignal.
Allen (CLE) does not deliver contact to Brooks (MEM) as he establishes himself in a screening position.
Brooks (MEM) gets to ball height and cleanly blocks Garland's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt.
